/02a.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7baU59XuI_text","label":"gg7baU59XuI_text","default":"<p>FULL SUSPENSIONS</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9qa_xi32i_text","label":"gg9qa_xi32i_text","default":"<p>The <strong>TRAIL</strong> X electric dirt bike uses a rear nitrogen shock and 230mm front hydraulic fork to absorb bumps, reduce fatigue, and keep young riders comfortable and in control.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGA_EgZdUs_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggGA_EgZdUs_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0540/8820/4467/files/03a.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXikryPmvg_text","label":"ggXikryPmvg_text","default":"<p>DUAL HYDRAULIC BRAKES</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtuCRTDpUI_text","label":"ggtuCRTDpUI_text","default":"<p>The <strong>TRAIL</strong> X electric dirt bike combines <strong>EABS</strong> and <strong>hydraulic disc brakes</strong> for smooth, reliable stopping—on any terrain.</p><p>Responsive braking builds control—and confidence.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1391qN7MO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg1391qN7MO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0540/8820/4467/files/04a_b6c0c125-6398-4a1c-9c17-f04c90cf126a.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv3qf1QyTK_text","label":"ggv3qf1QyTK_text","default":"<p>12\"&amp;14\"FAT TIRES</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggddUlK3Etx_text","label":"ggddUlK3Etx_text","default":"<p>The <strong>TRAIL</strong> X electric dirt bike features rugged 12” and 14” off-road tires for exceptional grip and stability. Engineered specifically to handle dirt, sand, and rugged terrain— delivering superior traction, a smoother ride, and confident control.</p>"}],
